    "2848:16": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:17": "none“> asti mahad rikthaṃ bauddhanaiyāyikānāṃ bhāratīyapramāṇamīmāṃsāśastrāṇāṃ",
    "2848:18": "samudbhāvane saṃvikāse samupabṛṃhaṇe ca |",
    "2848:19": "ramāṇamīmāṃsakeṣu bauddhataditarayoḥ",
    "2848:20": "katarasmin sampradāye idamprathamatayā pramāṇaśāstraṃ prādurbhāvamabhajaditi",
    "2848:21": "pracurapramāṇānupalabdheradyāpi nirṇetuṃ naiva śakyam |",
    "2848:22": "gautamīya - ūrvapakṣasūtreṣvanāhāryotthāpitānāṃ pratyakṣādyaprāmāṇya - traikālyakhaṇḍanavyaktipadārthatva - samarthanānātmatvābhāvādbhāvotpatti - kṣaṇabhaṅgatvānīśvaratvānavayavitvavi - jñānamātratvādibauddhavādānāṃ",
    "2848:23": "tattatsaugatatantreṣu tattatparyavasitarūpāṇāṃ paryālocanayā pramāṇa - premayavikāsasamīkṣayā ca vidyābhūṣaṇa - dāsaguptādiparikalpito bauddhapramāṇacarcāyā",
    "2848:24": "nyāyasūtrottarabhāvitvasiddhānto na nrigalito bhavati |",
    "2848:25": "pūrvapakṣasūtreṣu",
    "2848:26": "kathañcit purātanāsadvijñānavādasthitikalpanāpi śūnya - vijñānavādapravartakatvenākhyāta - nāgārjunamaitreyāsaṅgavasubandhuprabhṛtīnāṃ nyāyasūtrottarabhāvitvamanorathaṃ",
    "2848:27": "na pūrayati |",
    "2848:28": "śūnyavijñānānātmatirikta - pūrvoktasūtrasthavādāstatratyasaugatatantrasiddhāntapradaprāptā",
    "2848:29": "ātmānaṃ nirāyāsaṃ nyāyasūtra - pratipādita - siddhāntebhyo'pi prāktanatvaṃ",
    "2848:30": "dyotayanti ,",
    "2848:31": "saṃbhavayanti ca nyāyasūtrānapekṣi - sarvāstivādasammatapramāṇaprameyādikhaṇḍanaiḥ",
    "2848:32": "nāgārjunādīnāṃ sarvanāstitvavāda - sāfalyam ,",
    "2848:33": "sarvāstivāda - mādhyamikādimatāpekṣitvaṃ ca nyāyasūtrapūrvapakṣavādānām",
    "2848:34": "| yā hi vigrahavyāvarttanyām tadvṛttau ca pūrvapakṣatvena samupalabdhā catuṣpramāṇacarcā ,",
    "2848:35": "sā svodgamaprasthānamanviṣantī ,",
    "2848:36": "adyāpyasamañjameva niravakāśā bhramati |",
    "2848:37": "nyāyasūtrakṛt",
    "2848:38": "tadbhāṣyakṛt - tadvārtikakṛt - tattātparyakṛdbhiḥ svaprasthāne yo'ṅgīkāraḥ",
    "2848:39": "samupalabhyate ,",
    "2848:40": "sa tadvirodhenānyakalpane",
    "2848:41": "viśiṣṭabādhakapramāṇopalabdhimantarā naiva vidvatsahaḥ |",
    "2848:42": "suviditameva bauddhanāṃ",
    "2848:43": "tarkānurodhitvaṃ śruti - smṛtyanuyāyināṃ ca prācīnavaidika - dārśanikānāṃ tadvirodhitvamiti | tadevam",
    "2848:44": "anurodhitvena bauddheṣu tarkāṇāṃ purvabhāvaḥ ,",
    "2848:45": "tatprabhāvād gautamīyādiṣu paścādbhāvo nāsamañjasaḥ",
    "2848:46": "pratīyate | bhavatu vā aitihāsikānāṃ sambhāvanāmaṇḍito yathā - tathā - vādaḥ ,",
    "2848:47": "na tasyeha idānīṃ prāsaṅgikatvam |",
    "2848:48": "saugatapramāṇaśāstraṇāṃ",
    "2848:49": "parīkṣayā kāṇādagautamīyaiḥ samaṃ saugatakṛta - vāda - jalpa - vitaṇḍākathānāṃ paurvāparyopajīvakopajīvyabhāvasamīkṣayā",
    "2848:50": "tu saprakāśaṃ mayā prakāśanīyaḥ |",
