    "2848:57": "none“> brahyajālīyaparapravādān parīkṣitum ,",
    "2848:58": "parirakṣituṃ ca duḥkhanirodhagāminīṃ pratipad",
    "2848:59": "viśuddhiṃ bhagavatā buddhena sarvasaṃskārāṇām anityatvabodhāya ,",
    "2848:60": "sarvaduḥkhānāṃ ca antakaraṇāya ,",
    "2848:61": "śīlasamādhyorapi jananīva utpādayitrī pālayitrī",
    "2848:62": "ca mahāprajñā prajñāpāramitā puraskṛtā |",
    "2848:63": "prajñāprāmāṇyodbodhanāya vaiśālyāṃ kūṭāgāraśālāyāmudīritaṃ",
    "2848:64": "na tāvāhaṃ pāpima ,",
    "2848:65": "parinibbāyissāmi yāva me",
    "2848:66": "bhikkhū uppannaṃ parapvādaṃ sahadhammena suniggahitaṃ niggahetvā sapāṭihāriyaṃ",
    "2848:67": "dhammaṃ desisantī ' ti ( udāne 6 / 9 )",
    "2848:68": "bhagavadvacanaṃ praśasyataramiva bhavati |",
    "2848:69": "etadgarbhikṛtamidam aṣṭasāhasnikāvacanamapi samyagavadheyaṃ bhavati - praġyāpāramitaiva āyuṣmana sāriputra ,",
    "2848:70": "sārvayānikī ' iti |",
    "2848:71": "kiṃ bahunā , ' yatkiñcidudayadharmakaṃ tannirodhadharmakam ' yaṃ kiṃci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ",
    "2848:72": "nirodhadhammaṃ ' ti ( udāne 5 / 3 )",
    "2848:73": "nāhamekadharmamapi anabhijñāyāpariġyāya duḥkhasyāntakriyāṃ",
    "2848:74": "vadāmī ( a . ko . bhā . 1 / 15 )",
    "2848:75": "tyādibuddhavacanāni sfuṭameva",
    "2848:76": "vyaptyanumitigarbhāṃ kathām udāharanti |",
    "2848:77": "nityāgamapratipāditamarthaṃ na",
    "2848:78": "bahumanyamānāḥ śraddhāprajñayośca ' prajñāpradhānaṃ tvanayo ' rityādināgārjunādivacanaiḥ ( ratnāvalī - 5 )",
    "2848:79": "prajñāyā eva prādhānyamityudghoṣayanto",
    "2848:80": "bauddhadārśanikā avidyā - pratipakṣatvena aṅgībhūtāyāṃ",
    "2848:81": "madhyamāyāṃ pratipadi prathamatvena ca anubhavāvasānāṃ samyagdṛṣṭirūpāṃ vidyāṃ",
    "2848:82": "puraskurvanti |",
    "2848:83": "eṣa prajñāpuraskāra evotsabhūmiḥ bauddhapramāṇaśāstrāṇām |",
    "2848:84": "prajñāparāṇāṃ saugatānāṃ pramāṇavyasanitvaṃ sahajenaiva sambhāvayituṃ śakyaṃ",
    "2848:85": "yena lokottaravādibhistaiḥ diṅgnāgapramukhaiḥ śūnyatādvayādhigamarūpasya",
    "2848:86": "dharmakāyabhūtasya buddhasyaiva pramāṇarūpatvam ,",
    "2848:87": "tasyaiva ca ' prajñāpāramitā - jñānamadvayaṃ sa tathāgatah ' ( prajñāpāramitā - piṇḍārthaḥ )",
    "2848:88": "ityādivacanaiḥ advayajñānarūpatvaṃ vyavasthāpya",
    "2848:89": "pamāṇabhūtāya jagaddhitaiṣiṇe ( pra . sa . 1 / 1 )",
    "2848:90": "ityādibhiḥ satyacatuṣṭayāvisaṃvādine tasmai",
    "2848:91": "namaskāro'bhihitaḥ dharmakīrttinā ca pramāṇavārttikaprathamaparicchedapratipādyena",
    "2848:92": "avisaṃvādanāt bhagavataḥ pramāṇabhūtatvamiti vyākhyātam |",
    "2848:93": "etatsarvam",
    "2848:94": "abhiprotyoktaṃ prajñākāramatinā bhagavataḥ pramāṇabhūtatvamiti vyākhyātam |",
    "2848:95": "etatsarvam abhiprotyoktaṃ prajñākāramatinā pramāṇavārttikālaṅkārabhāṣye ( pṛ 116 )",
    "2848:96": "pramāṇādeva samastasiddhiriti pratipādayatā -",
