    "2848:117": "none“> evaṃ pramāṇabhūtatvaṃ buddhatve prayojakam",
    "2848:118": "adhigatya , sakalamapi bauddhaprasthānaṃ",
    "2848:119": "sākṣāt paramparayā vā pramāṇamīmāṃsāyāmeva paryavasitaṃ bhavati | evaṃ",
    "2848:120": "satyasmin laghukāyanibandhe saugatasammataṃ jñānasvarūpaṃ samāsena mīyate ,",
    "2848:121": "prasaṅgena tu kāṇādaṃ gautamīyaṃ cāpi kiṃcid",
    "2848:122": "nirdiśyate |",
    "2848:123": "normal;mso-pagination:",
