    "2848:128": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:129": "none“> arthākriyāvirahiṇo nityasya jñānasyāprāmāṇyam ,",
    "2848:130": "anityayā vastusaṅgatāyā eva dhiyaḥ prāmāṇyamiti",
    "2848:131": "bauddhapramāṇacintāyā abhimatam |",
    "2848:132": "avisaṃvāditve sati ajñātārthaprakāśakatva",
    "2848:133": "miti pramāṇalakṣaṇaṃ bahyetarobhayavādisammataṃ paramārthasaṃvṛtibhyāṃ dvidhā",
    "2848:134": "bhinnam | paramārthato'dvaitabodhasyājñātārthaprakāśarūpasya avisaṃvādanāt saṃvṛtisataḥ",
    "2848:135": "pratyakṣānumānābhyāṃ sākṣāt paramparayā vā ajñātasvalakṣaṇakānāmavisaṃvāditvena",
    "2848:136": "jñāpanād , dvayoḥ pramāṇyaṃ sidhyati",
    "2848:137": "| arthakriyāsamartha yad ityādi prasiddhapramāṇavārtikavacanaṃ ( 2 / 3 )",
    "2848:138": "sautrāntikānāṃ bāhyasadvastuvādaṃ vijñānavādināṃ",
    "2848:139": "vijñānaparamārthādvaitavādamanudhāvati |",
    "2848:140": "ubhayathāpi ca prāmāṇyāyā dhiyo",
    "2848:141": "vastusaṃgitatvaṃ ca virūdhyati |",
    "2848:142": "arthapakṣapāntinyā asyā buddheḥ pramāṇyāya",
    "2848:143": "bauddhaiḥ sarvaprathamaṃ jñeyasvarūpacintā vidhīyate ,",
    "2848:144": "sandhīyate ca pramāṇavyavasthāyastadeva",
    "2848:145": "prayojakaṃ tattvamiti |",
    "2848:146": "ata eva vastuvādisammataḥ meyādhīnā mānasiddhi ritipakṣaḥ",
    "2848:147": "siddhāntinto bhavati |",
    "2848:148": "vijñānavāde tu meyena mānavyavasthā yadyapyadhigatā ,",
    "2848:149": "tathāpi meyaṃ mānādhīnamiti siddhānto'pi",
    "2848:150": "paryavasyati |",
    "2848:151": "sahopalambhaniyamād vastubodhe mānaprādhānyamaṅgīkṛtyaiva vijñānavādibhiḥ",
    "2848:152": "saṃkalaṃ bāhyaṃ meyajātamapahatya mānaśeṣatā nītā |",
    "2848:153": "mānānurodhena viṣayavyavasthāṃ",
    "2848:154": "prasthāpayadbhiḥ kāṇādagautamīyaiḥ darśanasparśanāmyāmekārthagrahaṇā - ditinyāyāt sthiravati anyatamaprameye anekeṣāṃ",
    "2848:155": "pramāṇānām samavāyaḥ ekena ca pramāṇenanekeṣāṃ grahaṇamiti pramāṇasaṃplavavadaḥ",
    "2848:156": "prastūyate |",
    "2848:157": "eṣa ca saṃplavaḥ pramāṇam prameyaṃ cāviśeṣeṇa aniyataṃ saṃplutaṃ",
    "2848:158": "ca karoti | bauddhaistvatra viplavapakṣa āsañjitastadnurūpameva teṣāṃ svalakṣaṇa - sāmānyalakṣaṇābhyāṃ viṣayadvaividhyam pratyakṣānumānābhyāṃ",
    "2848:159": "ca pramāṇadvaividhyaṃ paryavasyati ,",
    "2848:160": "uktam pramāṇavartike mānaṃ dvividhaṃ viṣayadvaividhyāt",
    "2848:161": "( 2 / 1 ) tryekasaṃkhyānirāso va prameyadvayadarśanāt ( 2 / 64 ) ityādi |",
