    "2848:167": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:168": "none“> asti vastuviṣaye sāmānya - viśeṣābhyāṃ tadubhayamilitarūpābhyāṃ ca bauddhetarayorvipratipattiḥ",
    "2848:169": "| kāṇādagautamīyeṣu sāmānya - viśeṣa - tadvadbhedāttridhātvena na",
    "2848:170": "pramāṇa - prameyadvitve ,",
    "2848:171": "nāpi prameyeṣva - sāṃkarya pramāṇānām ,",
    "2848:172": "uktam udyotakarīyavārttike na tāvat pramāṇadvayaṃ",
    "2848:173": "pratipadyāmahe ,",
    "2848:174": "na viṣayadvayam ,",
    "2848:175": "nāpyasaṅkaramiti |",
    "2848:176": "bauddhamate tu sāmānya - viśeṣābhyām asaṃkīrṇarūpābhyām arthakriyātaddvirūddhābhyāṃ",
    "2848:177": "vastunaḥ svabhāvadvaividhyam ,",
    "2848:178": "tadvaśāt prameyadvitvaṃ sammataṃ bhavati |",
    "2848:179": "vastutastu bauddhamate",
    "2848:180": "sāmānyasyāpi vastutvam āpātaramyameva |",
    "2848:181": "buddhāvākārārpaṇa kṣamatvāt tasyaiva cārthakriyākāritvāt",
    "2848:182": "viśeṣasyaiva vastutvaṃ ,",
    "2848:183": "na sāmānyasya ukta mmeyaṃ",
    "2848:184": "tvekaṃ svalakṣaṇaṃ tasmādarthakriyāsiddhe riti evaṃ satyapi na sarvathā nirālambanaḥ",
    "2848:185": "sāmānya vyavahāraḥ |",
    "2848:186": "viśeṣasyaiva anugatākāratvena sāmānyapratīteḥ ,",
    "2848:187": "tasyaiva ca jñeyasvalakṣaṇarūpatvena samānatayā",
    "2848:188": "sāmānyasvīkārācca |",
    "2848:189": "viśeṣa eva yato vijātīyavyāvṛttyāśrayaḥ ,",
    "2848:190": "ataḥ sa evānugatākārabuddhayā sādhāraṇarūpatayā",
    "2848:191": "bhāsetātra na citram |",
    "2848:192": "uktamalaṅkārabhāṣye'pi yadā sākṣājjñānajananaṃ prati śaktatvena",
    "2848:193": "pratīyate , tadā'sau svarūpeṇa lakṣyamāṇatvāt",
    "2848:194": "svalakṣaṇam ,",
    "2848:195": "yadā tu pāramparyeṇa śaktatvāttasyaiva",
    "2848:196": "pratīti tadā sāmānyarūpeṇa lakṣaṇamiti sāmānyalakṣaṇam |",
    "2848:197": "pāramparyeṇa śaktirevāśaktiḥ",
    "2848:198": "paryudāsavṛttyā ,",
    "2848:199": "na śaktayabhāva eveti |",
    "2848:200": "yataścārthakriyārūpatvena viśeṣa eva vastuna svarūpam atastadevāvisaṃvādanāt paramārthasadapi",
    "2848:201": "| evaṃ sthite asataḥ sāmānyalakṣaṇasyāsatvaṃ svalakṣaṇāśrayatvenaiva yatastad",
    "2848:202": "bhāsate ataḥ pararūpeṇa bhāsamānaṃ vikalpenaiva ca kevalaṃ vyavahāryaūpaṃ",
    "2848:203": "bibhrat tat saṃvṛtyaiva sattvāt saṃvṛtisad bhavati |",
    "2848:204": "evaṃ yato hi aparamārthena",
    "2848:205": "asadbhūenāpi lokavyavahāraḥ saṃvādyata eva ,",
    "2848:206": "ataḥ sa satyamiva satyam |",
    "2848:207": "pararūpeṇa",
    "2848:208": "bhavadidaṃ sattvaṃ yathā bhāvāśrayaṃ tathā bhāva vāsanāprasūtavikalpakalpitatvād",
    "2848:209": "ahāvāśrayam ,",
    "2848:210": "bhāvābhāvāśrayaṃ cāpi",
    "2848:211": "siddhyati | yadyapyasti trividhasyāpi sāmānyasyāviśeṣena asattvameva ,",
    "2848:212": "tathāpi bhāvopādānatvena svabhāvahetoḥ ,",
    "2848:213": "abhāvopādānatvenānupalabdhihetoḥ ,",
    "2848:214": "ubhayopādānatvena kāryahetoḥ sattvamadhigatya",
    "2848:215": "trividhairapi hetubhistattvamadhigamyata eva |",
    "2848:216": "dvicandrādīnāṃ sattvaṃ tu",
    "2848:217": "jñeyatvādipararūpeṇāpi na siddhyati ,",
    "2848:218": "ato na kathamapyanarthabhūtānāṃ teṣāṃ sattvam",
    "2848:219": "| uktaṃ pramāṇavārtike - keśādayo na sāmānyamanarthābhiniveśataḥ",
    "2848:220": "iti |",
