    "2848:226": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:227": "none“> evaṃ caikasyaiva sataḥ svarūpa - pararūpābhyāṃ sva - sāmānyalakṣaṇābhyāṃ yathā viṣayadvayavyavasthā ,",
    "2848:228": "tathaiva svalakṣaṇamevaikaṃ pratyakṣānumānābhyāṃ",
    "2848:229": "dvābhyāmapi viṣayikriyate |",
    "2848:230": "ataeva yat svalakṣaṇarūpaṃ dṛśyaṃ ,",
    "2848:231": "yacca sāmānyasvarūpaṃ vikalpyaṃ ,",
    "2848:232": "te ubhe ekīkṛtyaiva lokavyavahāraḥ pravartate",
    "2848:233": "| sāmānyalakṣaṇaṃ vastutvena bhāsamānaṃ sadapi svalakṣaṇatvenāvasīyamānaṃ",
    "2848:234": "vastuviṣayaṃ pravṛttiviṣayaṃ ca bhavati |",
    "2848:235": "ata eva bāhyasambaddhatvena pratyakṣasya",
    "2848:236": "bāhyasambaddhasambaddhetvenānumānasya saṃvādakatvaṃ pramāṇyaṃ ca sammataṃ",
    "2848:237": "bhavati | etat sakalamabhipretyoktaṃ dharmottareṇa punarāropito'rtho gṛhyamāṇaḥ",
    "2848:238": "svalakṣaṇatvenāvasīyate yataḥ ,",
    "2848:239": "tataḥ svalakṣaṇamavasitaṃ pravṛttiviṣayo'numānasyeti | tatra",
    "2848:240": "durvekeṇa coktam tasmānna dvividho viṣayaḥ pramāṇasyābhidhānīyo'pitveka eva",
    "2848:241": "pravṛttiviṣayo'sya khyāpanīya iti evaṃ ekasyaiva ca tasya ratipattiprakārabheda",
    "2848:242": "evāyaṃ pramāṇabhedasya prayojako nānyaḥ |",
    "2848:243": "evaṃ ca paramārthabhūtaṃ yatsvalakṣaṇākhyaṃ",
    "2848:244": "prameyaṃ tadevaikaṃ pramāṇasya grāhyamiti paryavasyati ,",
    "2848:245": "taddhi anadhyavaseyamanabhidheyantattvam |",
    "2848:246": "pramāṇādhyavaseyaṃ tu kevalaṃ pararūpaṃ sāmānyameva |",
    "2848:247": "evaṃ ca paramārthasaṃvṛttibhyāmapi",
    "2848:248": "pramāṇaprameyadvayavyavasthā sarvabauddhairadhigatā bhavati |",
    "2848:249": "itthaṃ sautrāntikanaye",
    "2848:250": "yathā paramārthasaṃvṛtyoḥ prameyaprayojakatvenāṅgīkārastathā pramāṇadvitvaprayojakatvenāpi",
    "2848:251": "viniyogī na kathamapyasamañjasaḥ |",
    "2848:252": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:253": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:254": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:255": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:256": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:257": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:258": "none“> yo hyayaṃ svalakṣaṇākhyaḥ asādhāraṇaḥ svabhāva",
    "2848:259": "uktaḥ ṣa vastuvādibauddhamate paramāṇureva |",
    "2848:260": "paramāṇuvādaśca abhidharmakośālambanaparīkṣādyanurodhena",
    "2848:261": "vaibhāṣikasautrāntikamateṣu parasparamanati - bhedabhinneṣu dravyaparamāṇu - saṃghātaparamāṇusaṃcitākāraparamāṇuvādābhidhānaiḥ",
    "2848:262": "bhidyante | aviśeṣeṇa yadyapi paramāṇavo'tīndriyā eva bhavanti ,",
    "2848:263": "tathāpyaṇu - saṃghāta - saṃcayādibhiḥ aṣṭa - nava - daśaikādaśādīnāṃ sahotpādāt teṣu sparśavattvaṃ",
    "2848:264": "siddhyati | sparśavattvam aṇutvavyāpyamiti svayūthya - siddhāntamaṅgīkṛtya ,",
    "2848:265": "anaṅgīkṛtyāpi kāṇāda - gautamasammatam avayavivādaṃ saṃhateṣu paramaṇuṣveva",
    "2848:266": "sthaulyādeḥ pratītiḥ svīkṛtā |",
    "2848:267": "uktatrividhānitya - paramāṇuvādiṣu atītānāgatākālasattāyā apākaraṇāt",
    "2848:268": "sautrāntika eva pradhānapadaṃ bibharti ,",
    "2848:269": "yena tatpratipādita - kṣaṇabhaṅgavāda - kṣaṇasantativādābhyāṃ vastunaḥ sūkṣmatamaṃ",
    "2848:270": "svalakṣaṇarūpaṃ prajñaptisacca sāntānikaṃ rūpaṃ prakāśatāṃ gacchati | savavyāpi",
    "2848:271": "cāyaṃ sautrāntikasammato dravyaparamāṇuḥ anityaḥ ,",
    "2848:272": "deśataḥ kālataḥ svarūpataśca vicchinnaḥ ,",
    "2848:273": "svatantraśceti sampannaḥ kṣaṇaparamāṇureṣaḥ",
    "2848:274": "santānarāśyādirūpeṇa jñāyate ,",
    "2848:275": "yatra daiśikaṃ kālikaṃ karmafalādikaṃ sambandhataḥ prakarṣataśca",
    "2848:276": "paripuṣṭaṃ sad bhāsate |",
    "2848:277": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:278": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:279": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:280": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:281": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:282": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:283": "none“> etādṛśaparamāṇuvādasvīkārādeva vastuvādino",
    "2848:284": "bauddhastīrthikabāhyārthavādibhyo vyāvṛttā bhavanti |",
    "2848:285": "ayaṃ ca vyāvṛttiprakāraḥ",
    "2848:286": "prameye pramāṇaviṣaye ca samānameva paryavasito bhavati |",
    "2848:287": "vaiśeṣikanaye paramāṇurnityaḥ",
    "2848:288": ", sthiro dvyaṇukādikrameṇārabdhasyāvayavinaḥ",
    "2848:289": "samavāyikāraṇam ,",
    "2848:290": "guṇakarma - viśeṣādīnāmāśrayaḥ |",
    "2848:291": "bauddhābhimatastu paramāṇuḥ",
    "2848:292": "atīndriyo'pi pratyutpannakālamātra - sattvāt kṣaṇabhaṅgaḥ ,",
    "2848:293": "tasmādanityaḥ ,",
    "2848:294": "guṇakarmādīnāmanāśrayo'navayavirūpaḥ siddhyati",
    "2848:295": "| evaṃ ca bauddhasammata - paramāṇusvīkāreṇa gautamakaṇādāṅgīkṛtaṃ",
    "2848:296": "rūpādyatiriktaṃ rūpādyadhiṣṭhānam ekapratyayahetu avayavidravyam ,",
    "2848:297": "aparāparadeśotpannahastādikṣaṇād bhinnaṃ karma ,",
    "2848:298": "vyaktivyatireki sāmānyaṃ ceti vādā nirākṛtā",
    "2848:299": "bhavanti | ata eva nyāyavaiśeṣikābhimatāḥ sarvā api dravya - guṇa - karmādipratītayo bauddhamatenānādivāsanālakṣaṇāntarakāraṇanibandhāḥ",
    "2848:300": "prajñaptimātrāṇi ,",
    "2848:301": "na tā arthadhīnāḥ | evaṃ",
    "2848:302": "yadyapyayaṃ nityaparamāṇuvādaḥ vaiśeṣikaparamparānuprāptastathāpi tebhyaḥ ayāttīkṛtya",
    "2848:303": "kṣaṇabhaṃgāpattyā pūrvabauddhairjīrṇīkṛtaḥ ,",
    "2848:304": "paravarttibhiśca vijñānapade saṃsthāpyā'sau jaḍāṇuścetanābhāsīkṛtaḥ",
    "2848:305": "| cetanā - bhāsībhūtasyāsya paramāṇoḥ",
    "2848:306": "svarūpaṃ svasaṃviditaṃ saṃ bāhyapadārthānanabhyupagacchāṃ navyabauddhānāṃ kṛte",
    "2848:307": "jñānasyānāsravaṃ jaḍanirmuktaṃ cādvaitasvarūpaṃ prakaṭayati |",
    "2848:308": "itthaṃ bauddhānāṃ",
    "2848:309": "ābhāsavapuḥparamāṇu - cintayā anābhāsairbāhyajaḍairjaḍīkṛtamiva",
    "2848:310": "pramāṇadvāramapākṛtya pramātvavyākaraṇāya bāhyaśūnyaṃ sābhāsaṃ saviśadamadhigamamārgam",
    "2848:311": "avātarata | ayaṃ ca vādo yathāsthānaṃ viśadīkarīṣyate |",
    "2848:312": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:313": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:314": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:315": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:316": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:317": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:318": "none“> jñānānaṃ nirākāratva - sākāratvavaśādapi tadālambanasya vastunaḥ",
    "2848:319": "sattvaṃ prakaṭitaṃ bhavati ,",
    "2848:320": "vijñātaṃ ca bhavati jñānasya svarūpam ,",
    "2848:321": "tatpramātvam ,",
    "2848:322": "tadavabodhaprakāraśca |",
    "2848:323": "sarve'pi bāhyārthavādino",
    "2848:324": "bauddhābauddhadārśanikā vaiśeṣika - vaibhāṣika - sautrāntika - gautamīyā jñānanirākāravādino bhavanti | teṣāṃ",
    "2848:325": "mate jñānānāṃ nirākāratvavaśādapi vastunaḥ sattvaṃ prakaṭitaṃ bhavati ,",
    "2848:326": "viditaśca bhavati jñānasya svarūpāvabodhahetuḥ",
    "2848:327": "| uktaṃ ca sarve'pi bāhyārtha - vastuvādino bauddhābauddhadārśanikā jñānanirākāratvavādinaḥ santi",
    "2848:328": "| teṣāṃ mate yo'yaṃ jñāne ākāraḥ pratibhāsate ,",
    "2848:329": "sa grāhakajñānād vyatiriktasya sthirasya kṣaṇikasya",
    "2848:330": "vā grāhyabhūtasya arthasyaiva |",
    "2848:331": "ata eva abauddhanaiyāyikaiḥ pratyakṣasthale nirākārajñānāt",
    "2848:332": "tadviprakṛṣṭam artham bodhayituṃ indriyārthayoḥ sannikarṣaḥ ,",
    "2848:333": "vaibhāṣikasautrāntikaiśca viṣayendriyavijñānānāṃ",
    "2848:334": "trikasparśaḥ manyate |",
    "2848:335": "sakalasarvāstivādibauddhānāṃ trikasparśavāditve samāne'pi",
    "2848:336": "asti arthagrahaṇa - arthasārūpyābhyāṃ trikālaikakālavāditvābhyāṃ",
    "2848:337": "ca bhedaḥ | tato'rthājjātaṃ pratyakṣa miti vāsubāndhavapratyakṣa - lakṣaṇāt pūrvataḥ sata eva arthasya grahaṇaṃ jñāpyate ,",
    "2848:338": "kṣaṇaikakālamātrasthitasya paramāṇoḥ vijñānasya",
    "2848:339": "ya sarūpaṇamiti sautrāntikapakṣo'ṅgīkriyate |",
    "2848:340": "itthaṃ sanniakrṣatrikasparśayoḥ",
    "2848:341": "bhede vastunaḥ sthiratva - kṣaṇikatve eva prayojake",
    "2848:342": "| jñāne pratimāsamāna ākāra eva vastunaḥ arthakriyā ,",
    "2848:343": "eṣa eva ca vastunaḥ sattvam &lt;",
    "2848:344": "etadadhigamenaiva dhiyaḥ saṃvāditvam ,",
    "2848:345": "saṃvāditvācca pramāṇyaṃ svīkṛtam |",
    "2848:346": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:347": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:348": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:349": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:350": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:351": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:352": "none“> evaṃ ca pratyakṣānumānayoḥ dvayorapi sākṣāt",
    "2848:353": "paramparayā vā aviśeṣato vastvadhigamena avisaṃvādanāt prāmāṇyaṃ siddhyati |",
    "2848:354": "yadyapi abauddhanaiyāyikairapi dhiyo nirākāratayā arthenaiva viśeṣo manyate ,",
    "2848:355": "kintu arthakriyākāritvena vastunaḥ sattvamanaṅgīkṛtya ,",
    "2848:356": "taiḥ jñānārthendriyāṇām ekakālikatvakṣaṇasattvapakṣaḥ",
    "2848:357": "apahastitaḥ |",
    "2848:358": "ata eva teṣāṃ mate pūrvakālato vartamānayoḥ indriyārthayoḥ ,",
    "2848:359": "avayavisatoḥ ,",
    "2848:360": "saṃyogena trikṣaṇāvasthāyinoḥ jñānagunasyotpādaḥ",
    "2848:361": "siddhāntasiddho bhavati |",
    "2848:362": "kāṇādagautamīyānāṃ nirākāravāditve'pi kṣaṇasattva - virodhād dravyaguṇakarmāṇi parāparātmakarūpeṇa",
    "2848:363": "sāmānyaviśeṣātmakāni jñāyante |",
    "2848:364": "tatra ca anekeṣāṃ pramāṇāṃ saṃplavo'pi na virūddhyate",
    "2848:365": "| bauddhamate tu viśeṣamātraṃ vastu ,",
    "2848:366": "tadgrāhakaṃ ca kevalaṃ pratyakṣam ,",
    "2848:367": "tadbhinnaṃ sarvamapi prātitikaṃ sāmānyamātram ,",
    "2848:368": "tadgrāhakaṃ cānumānamiti pṛṣṭhabhāvi - vikalpa iti ca pakṣamaṃgīkṛtya asaṃkīrṇa pramāṇaṃ - prameyaṃ ca saṃsthāpya paraparikalpitapramāṇāni",
    "2848:369": "dvayorevāntaḥ vilīyante |",
    "2848:370": "bauddhānāṃ cāyaṃ pramāntarbhāvaprakaraḥ tato'rvācīnaiḥ",
    "2848:371": "prayāśaḥ sakalairapi vedānugaiḥ nyāyadarśanakāraiḥ icchayā anicchayā vā avaśyasamarthanīyo",
    "2848:372": "jātaḥ , anyāni ca pramāṇāni taiḥ",
    "2848:373": "anumāne antarbhāvitāni evaṃ ca bauddhamatena upamānaśabdārthāpattyanupalabdhi - pramāṇajātaṃ jñānanirākāravāditvea samāne'pi",
    "2848:374": "bauddhamate nirākāratvavaśād jñānasya svāṃśe nirvikalpatvam ,",
    "2848:375": "paramārthamātragrāhitvam ,",
    "2848:376": "jñānasya svaprakāśatvam ,",
    "2848:377": "pramāṇānāṃ ca prāyaśaḥ svataḥ pramāṇyamiti vādāḥ",
    "2848:378": "saprasaṅgaṃ samudbhāvitāḥ |",
    "2848:379": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:380": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:381": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:382": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:383": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:384": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:385": "none“> śāṅkaramate tu paramārthabhūtaṃ brahyaṃ pratyakṣagocaram ,",
    "2848:386": "taddhi nirvikalpakaṃ nirākāraṃ svaprakāśaṃ",
    "2848:387": "svataḥ pramāṇamiti bauddhapakṣamātmagatamiva kṛtvā svasañcchannaṃ saugatapramāṇanugatvaṃ",
    "2848:388": "vicchinnaṃ karoti |",
    "2848:389": "kiṃ bahunā , dravyaguṇakarmaṇāṃ nyāyaparikalpitalakṣaṇāni ,",
    "2848:390": "avayavi - sāmānya - samavāya - saṃyogādīnāṃ svarūpato nirāsaḥ pūrvatanaiḥ",
    "2848:391": "sautrāntikādibhiḥ kṛta eva brahyasūtra - tacchāṅkara - bhāṣyaṭīkādiṣu anukṛtaḥ bahudhā svaparibhāṣayā",
    "2848:392": "samarthitaśca |",
    "2848:393": "kimadhikena ,",
    "2848:394": "satyadvayaṃ trayaṃ vā ādhṛtya śaṃkarabhagavatpādaiḥ mithyāvādamūlo'dvaitavādo",
    "2848:395": "yo hi khyāpitaḥ sa sautrāntikānāṃ sva - samānyagatavastusattādvayavādasya anukaraṇamātrameva",
    "2848:396": "|",
    "2848:397": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:398": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:399": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:400": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:401": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:402": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:403": "none“> na tirohitaṃ yad bauddhamate yathā svalakṣaṇamāśrityaiva",
    "2848:404": "mithyābhūtaṃ sāmānyalakṣaṇaṃ vastutvena adhyavasīyate ,",
    "2848:405": "tathaiva brahyavāde brahyādhiṣṭhānakaṃ nānātvaṃ",
    "2848:406": "mithyābhūtamapi bhāsate |",
    "2848:407": "svalakṣaṇasya jñānātiriktatvena ānāntyena ca ,",
    "2848:408": "brahyaṇo jñānarūpatvena ekatvena ca yo hi āpātiko",
    "2848:409": "bhedo dṛśyate ,",
    "2848:410": "so'pi vijñānavāde asta",
    "2848:411": "iva jāyate | ayaṃ hi vistarabhiyā tyajyate |",
    "2848:412": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:413": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:414": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:415": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:416": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:417": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:418": "none“> astyanyo'pyavadheyo bauddhapramāṇamīmāṃsāyāḥ",
    "2848:419": "prakarṣaḥ | prāyaśo bāhyavastusiddhihetoreva pramāṇavyavasthā sarvereva bauddhābauddhavastuvādibhiḥ",
    "2848:420": "vikāsamāpāditā ,",
    "2848:421": "tenaiva ca nāgārjunāryadevādibhiḥ",
    "2848:422": "sarvāstivādasammato niṣkampo pramāṇaprameyavyavahāraḥ niḥsvabhāvatāvajraśilāyāṃ",
    "2848:423": "vikampito vikhaṇḍitaśca ,",
    "2848:424": "tadanusṛtya ca śāṅkarādvaitibhirapi",
    "2848:425": "śrīharṣacitsukhaprabhṛtibhiḥ sasāṃkhyolūkyādi - vastuvādaḥ sāṭopaṃ niḥśeṣatāṃ nītaḥ | satyasmin",
    "2848:426": "matapravāhe aticitraṃ bauddhanaiyāyikānām ,",
    "2848:427": "yattaiḥ vijñānavyatiriktaṃ pramātṛprameyadibāhyāsattvaṃ",
    "2848:428": "niṣedhayadbhirapi diṅnāga - dharmakīrttiprabhṛtibhiḥ",
    "2848:429": "vijñaptimātratāvaśād bhāratīyapramāṇaśāstraṃ nirbādhaṃ ṇyāyaprakarṣasya parāṃ",
    "2848:430": "koṭimāpāditam |",
    "2848:431": "etadabhinavaprasthānamanurūdhya vaidikaiḥ advaitavādibhiḥ",
    "2848:432": "svasvaprasthānānurodhipramāṇaśāstraṃ na ācaritam |",
    "2848:433": "ye tu arvācīnāḥ kecana",
    "2848:434": "granthā upalabhyante ,",
    "2848:435": "te prāyaḥ gautama - bhaṭṭa - prabhākarādīnāṃ nayānukaraṇamūlā eva |",
    "2848:436": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:437": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:438": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2848:439": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:440": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:441": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2848:442": "none“> āsīt ādau prameyāpekṣayaiva pramāṇasiddhivyavasthā ,",
    "2848:443": "tadanurodhenaiva ca dharmakīrttinā'pi svapramāṇavārtike",
    "2848:444": "bāhulyena sautrāntikābhimato vastusadvādaḥ aṅgīkṛta ityasti saugatābhiyuktānāṃ",
    "2848:445": "pāramparikam abhimatam |",
    "2848:446": "etanmatasya sārāvabodhaḥ bhoṭabhāṣāntaritānekavyākhyāgranthālocanaireva",
    "2848:447": "nirṇeyaḥ | vastutastu bāhyasattvāsattvobhayavādasaha evāyaṃ pramāṇaparo grantha",
    "2848:448": "iti pramāṇavārttikānurodhena samupalabdhamanorathanandivṛtti - alaṅkārabhāṣyālocanena ca pratīyate |",
    "2848:449": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2848:450": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2848:451": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
