    "2848:455": "none“> bāhyārthavādibhiḥ bāhyārthamantareṇa kāryakāraṇabhāvo",
    "2848:456": "jñāpyajñāpakabhāvaḥ tadabhāve ca anumānavyavahāro na svīkriyate ,",
    "2848:457": "kintu diṅnāgadharmakīrttiprabhṛtayaḥ pramāṇyavivecanāya",
    "2848:458": "vijñānavādaṃ yathā avirūddhamanukūlaṃ ca jānanti ,",
    "2848:459": "na tathā bāhyārthavādam |",
    "2848:460": "yadyapi bāhyārthasatprameyamapekṣyaiva jñānaprāmāṇyaprasaṃge",
    "2848:461": "arthakriyākāritvam ,",
    "2848:462": "arthaprāpakatvam ,",
    "2848:463": "arthādhyavasāyaḥ ,",
    "2848:464": "pratyakṣe indriyādi vijñānam ,",
    "2848:465": "anumāne liṅgaliṅginoḥ sambandhaḥ ,",
    "2848:466": "dhūmādagnibodhaścetyādikaṃ sampadyata iti āpātataḥ",
    "2848:467": "pratīyate , tathāpi etatsakalo'pi",
    "2848:468": "vyavahāraḥ yataḥ pratibhāsamūlatvenaiva loke prayujyate ,",
    "2848:469": "śāstre cāpi vicāryate |",
    "2848:470": "bāhyārthasvīkārapakṣe'pi",
    "2848:471": "pratibhāsabalādeva ca bāhyārtho'pi adhigato bhavati ,",
    "2848:472": "ato bāhyetaravādayoḥ samānarūpa eva pramāṇavicāro",
    "2848:473": "vijñānavādibhiḥ prastūyate |",
    "2848:474": "niyatākārabodhahetutve bāhyārtha eva prayojaka iti",
    "2848:475": "bāhyārthibhiḥ svīkriyate ,",
    "2848:476": "kintu bāhyo vā ,",
    "2848:477": "prabuddhavāsanāviśeṣo vā ,",
    "2848:478": "samanantarapratyayo vā prabodhakatvena niyāmakaḥ",
    "2848:479": "syādityanenāpi na kācid vyavahārabādhā |",
    "2848:480": "vijñānavādinaiyāyikaiḥ yā bāhyārthahcintā",
    "2848:481": "urarīkriyate ,",
    "2848:482": "sā na bāhyārthavyapekṣayā",
    "2848:483": "apitu dhiyo vinimayāpekṣayā tattvāvagāhinī bhavati |",
    "2848:484": "uktaṃ pramāṇavārtike tadupekṣitatattvārtheḥ bāhyacintā",
    "2848:485": "pratanyate ' iti ' kasyacit kiṃcidevāntarvāsanāyāḥ prayojakam |",
    "2848:486": "tato dhiyāṃ vinimayā na bāhyārthavyapekṣayā | | iti ca |",
