    "2848:493": "none“> ' upalambha eva vastusattā ' iti matamāmanadbhiḥ vijñānavādibhiḥ na arthena",
    "2848:494": "prayojanamaṅgīkriyate apitu pratibhāsenaiva |",
    "2848:495": "pratibhāso hi bāhyamantareṇaiva",
    "2848:496": "bhavati iti khyātameva |",
    "2848:497": "evaṃ sati dhūmādagnyanumāne dhūmapratibhāsā buddhiḥ",
    "2848:498": "agnivāsanāpratibaddhā satī ekapratyayasāmagrībalād agnibhāsāṃ dhiyaṃ janayati |",
    "2848:499": "vastutastu ācāryadharmakīrtimate vāsanaiva arthakriyākāritvena paramārthaḥ | sa",
    "2848:500": "ca pratibhāsarūpaḥ ,",
    "2848:501": "yo hi jñānasya paramārthato",
    "2848:502": "viṣayaḥ | bāhyārthavāde'pi bahisthaḥ tātkāliko bahnirna anumīyate ,",
    "2848:503": "ekasminkāle kāryakāraṇaparijñānābhāvāt apitu",
    "2848:504": "bhāvibhūtaḥ |",
    "2848:505": "bhāvibhūtaścāgniḥ pratibhāsarūpa eva |",
    "2848:506": "ata eva nahi apratibhāsena",
    "2848:507": "agninā pramāṇacarcāyāṃ kiṃcit prayojanaṃ siddhayati |",
    "2848:508": "evaṃ vāsanaiva bhāvipratibhāsā ,",
    "2848:509": "ekatayā ca pratīyamānā pravartikā bhavat |",
    "2848:510": "uktaṃ ca pramāṇavārtike -",
